title: Excel Decoder Agent Input/Output Data and MIM - MediationZone Documentation 9.3 - InfoZone
text: Input/Output Data Input/Output data is the type of data that an agent both recognizes and delivers. The Decompressor agent consumes bytearray types and delivers ExcelUDR s. MIM For information about the MIM and a list of the general MIM parameters, see MIM . The Excel Decoder agent only publishes and accesses MIMs of general type.
